{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make those convicted for domestic abuse ineligible for early release",
        "additional_details": "I am a survivor of horrific domestic abuse. I am worried that domestic abusers may end up only serving a fraction of their sentences. Victims should be allowed the time to heal before their abuser is released.",
        "background": "I want the Government to change the law so that people convicted of serious domestic abuse offences must serve their full prison sentence instead of being released early. ",
